## Overview

标签页容器组件，用于管理和切换多个标签页

## Properties

| Property | Attribute | Description | Type | Default |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `layer` | `layer` | 组件层级设置，影响样式和视觉层次 | `"01" \| "02" \| "background"` | `undefined` |
| `type` | `type` | 标签页类型，决定标签页的视觉样式 | `"contained" \| "contained-bottom" \| "default"` | `'default'` |
